data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of "Beautiful Hillandale"! This stunning All Brick 1940's Colonial sits gracefully on a spacious half-acre-plus lot, perched on a hillside, offering breathtaking views of the picturesque surroundings. With a blend of classic charm and modern upgrades, this residence is the epitome of timeless elegance.  Step inside to discover a meticulously maintained interior, featuring two fireplaces, providing warmth and ambiance throughout. The main level boasts a newly remodeled open-concept kitchen and dining area, complete with new floors and recessed LED lighting, a $60k investment that ensures a perfect blend of style and functionality.  The property's exterior is a true haven, surrounded by decks, trees, and a fenced backyard. Enjoy the serenity of the sunroom, featuring a built-in bench, perfect for unwinding and taking in the views. The expansive outdoor living space includes two decks, offering ample opportunities for entertaining or simply enjoying the beautiful weather.  Designed for comfort and convenience, offering two full and two half baths, along with custom upgrades such as a large pantry, custom-built laundry facilities, and an office laundry room renovation – a total investment of $18,750 in enhancing your daily living experience.  Key improvements include a new roof over the laundry room, basement carpeting, and comprehensive basement waterproofing with a French drain modification, totaling $7,800. The electrical upgrade ensures modern functionality and the landscaping investment of $7,000 adds to the property's curb appeal. Further enhancing the property's allure is its proximity to the FDA Campus, making it an ideal location for those working in the area. Convenient access to bus routes, including the new bus rapid transit (BRT) system under construction, adds to the property's value. Future developments, such as the redeveloped White Oak Center with additional restaurants and shopping, promise an even more vibrant and convenient lifestyle.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautifully updated colonial your new home. Owners do have a VA loan and are willing to do a VA Assumption.
